sentence: economy fares new york to miami round trip
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  v0.round_trip_cost, '"'||v1.fare_basis_code||'"',
 '"'||v1.economy||'"', '"'||v2.fare_id||'"', '"'||v3.flight_id||'"',
 '"'||v4.airport_code||'"', '"'||v5.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v5.city_name||'"', '"'||v6.airport_code||'"', '"'||v7.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v7.city_name||'"' FROM fare v0, fare_basis v1,
 flight_fare v2, flight v3, airport_service v4, city v5,
 airport_service v6, city v7 
WHERE ((v0.round_trip_cost IS NOT NULL) 
AND (((v0.fare_basis_code = ANY v1.fare_basis_code) 
AND (v1.economy = 'YES')) AND ((v0.fare_id = ANY v2.fare_id) 
AND ((v2.flight_id = ANY v3.flight_id) AND (((v3.from_airport = ANY v4.airport_code) 
AND ((v4.city_code = ANY v5.city_code) 
AND (v5.city_name = 'NEW YORK'))) AND ((v3.to_airport = ANY v6.airport_code) 
AND ((v6.city_code = ANY v7.city_code) 
AND (v7.city_name = 'MIAMI'))))))));
sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT FARE.FARE_ID FROM FARE WHERE ( FARE.ROUND_TRIP_COST IS NOT NULL AND ( FARE . FARE_BASIS_CODE IN ( SELECT FARE_BASIS . FARE_BASIS_CODE FROM FARE_BASIS WHERE FARE_BASIS.ECONOMY = ' YES ' ) AND FARE . FARE_ID IN ( SELECT FLIGHT_FARE . FARE_ID FROM FLIGHT_FARE WHERE FLIGHT_FARE . FLIGHT_ID IN ( SELECT FLIGHT . FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' NEW YORK ' ) ) AND FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' MIAMI ' ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ;
